{"tid":1722251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環男被警打至入ICU","createTime":"2019-11-15T00:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c98fc181a237ad4144dbd74fca1107896aaffd","tid":1722251,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191115/RKKDHJLEONNK6EXG2XRXPMEMHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191115%2FRKKDHJLEONNK6EXG2XRXPMEMHQ%2F&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=9ecb552b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191115%2FRKKDHJLEONNK6EXG2XRXPMEMHQ%2F&h=2f6f9284\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191115/RKKDHJLEONNK6EXG2XRXPMEMHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n中環男被警打至入ICU<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名26歲男子前日在中環交易廣場附近被警方拘捕時，遭警員暴打至頭破血流，其後被押到瑪麗醫院治理，其頭顱受傷，並有抽搐情況，經血管造影後確定有頭皮血腫。有知情醫護形容，有關傷勢很大可能是因頭部被棍打傷而成。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：若京出兵 即撤港獨立關稅地位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191115/large/1573752103_af59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191115%2Flarge%2F1573752103_af59.jpg&h=ed5128f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有傷者朋友昨在交易廣場舉牌，呼籲巿民若拍到事主被捕前後可與他們聯絡。互聯網<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫護：可能遭棍打傷頭<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該名26歲男子有抽搐情況，經血管造影及磁力共振檢查後，確診有頭皮血腫，但未有嚴重顱內出血。有知情醫護表示，傷者有抽搐的情況，很可能是與頭部受傷及腦部受挫傷，即被硬物撞擊有關，而他很可能頭部被棍打傷。該男子昨日仍然在深切治療部留醫，但相信應該可以康復。此外，過去數日，瑪麗醫院四樓病房外均有防暴警駐守，相信是看守其他被捕病人。<br />\n<br />\n該名26歲傷者的朋友表示，事主當時只是身穿黑衫黑褲，並沒有任何防具，他一度被防暴警員按落地下制服，其間頭破血流，但被反鎖手銬帶走時仍清醒，朋友懷疑他是被帶返警署後遭毒打致頭部重創，又擔心警方會插贓嫁禍，呼籲巿民若拍攝到事主被捕前後的情況，可以與他們聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳沛冰"},{"pid":"0e343338d981056e2d58d2fc91c5b6da149e1de3","tid":1722251,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"朋友的貓會朋友昨天...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"68ed1ebebc86a6c24a4ab78560a38eca77a84e2f","tid":1722251,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:28:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc97d023669df5302872d3dc6bdef0060a696cef","tid":1722251,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e343338d981056e2d58d2fc91c5b6da149e1de3","tid":1722251,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"朋友的貓會朋友昨天...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:31:39.000Z","msg":"昨天，佢個朋友嘅貓會朋友於"},{"pid":"031303c25ac0838ddc294ff4f3cfcfec73fbe3a7","tid":1722251,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:32:28.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"89d38bd0734d59108809ae944a6d774df67753cf","tid":1722251,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:34:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13a7462e56ea1757db845a53816b4d0d8edef47e","tid":1722251,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"476a5deed6e7b3d58cab1396e9407678e3b383bb","tid":1722251,"uid":291921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}